{"tid":883170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒大VS仁大 2間私立大學學費相差6.48萬元","createTime":"2018-10-30T15:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T15:34:30.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9aedc16bb21c1a107615b3043db205b27d3c0405","tid":883170,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"恒生管理學院獲行會通過升格為大學。現時恒管設5個學院，包括商科、傳播學、決策科學、人文社會科學及翻譯學，提供17個學士學位課程，包括較受歡迎的工商管理、新聞及傳播、文化及創意產業等，入學最低要求需中學文憑試中、英文3級或以上，數學、通識教育及一科選修科則需達2級。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n2018／19年入學的本地生4年學費為34.2萬元。</span></strong></span>   <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181030/58853439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58853439&d=GeIUBdKxD6J9w2hxUWaCUACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d28597b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58853439&h=62c67f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181030/58853439</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>貴到仆街</strong></span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}